**Slider is behaving incorrectly when entering a 4-digit value**

Platform:
 - OS: [Web]

Describe the bug
When the user enters a 4-digit value in the 'Desired Savings Amount' box, the slider moves all the way to the end and then resets to the correct position corresponding to the entered value. This commonly occurs when typing promptly.

To Reproduce
Steps to reproduce the behavior:
1. Go to 'https://bausparrechner.bausparen.at/rechner/'
2. Click on 'Desired savings amount' box and enter a 4-digit value promptly
3. View behaviour of the slider

Expected behavior
The slider moves to the correct position corresponding to the entered value.

Actual behavior
The slider moves all the way to the end and then resets to the correct position.

